<h1><span class="editsection">[<a href="/w/index.php?title=Sudo_room/Compact&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1" title="Edit section: The Compact">edit</a>]</span> <span class="mw-headline" id="The_Compact">The Compact</span></h1>
<h2><span class="editsection">[<a href="/w/index.php?title=Sudo_room/Compact&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2" title="Edit section: Ratification">edit</a>]</span> <span class="mw-headline" id="Ratification">Ratification</span></h2>
